Here we have a string of parentheses and we have to remove the outermost parentheses.
We will keep a count variable which will keep track of the number of open parentheses.
if the character is open parentheses then we will check if count is greater than 0 or not.
If yes then we will add the character to the answer list and then we will increment the count variable.
If the character is closed parentheses then we will decrement the count variable and then we will check if count is greater than 0 or not. 
If yes then we will add the character to the answer list.
Finally we will join the answer list and return the string.
